# Changelog

## Unreleased
### Fixes
- Grabbing explosives now also purchases ammo
- Saving a file now appends the correct file extension if none is given

### Changes
- Temporarily removed Flashlight and Binoculars from equipable weapons due to an issue with grabbing them that I can't find a cause for
- Added a Debug button that displays the macro's plaintext in a popup
- Debug builds now say `[DEBUG]` in the window title
- Automatically adds "Requires AutoHotkey v2.0" and "SingleInstance Force" to generated AHK scripts

## v0.1.0 - 2/21/2026
- Initial release